# Path to the local folder that contains your projects (outside this repo).
# Examples:
#   macOS/Linux: /Users/you/Projects
#   Windows:     C:\Users\you\Projects
#
# If you use phase-named subdirs (1.IDEA, 2.SCRATCH, 3.PROTOTYPE, 4.HML, 5.PROD, 6.ARCHIVED, 7.DROPPED),
# put this path at the parent of those folders. Otherwise, point directly to the folder
# that contains one subdir per project (phase will default to "idea").
BALCONY_TARGET_FOLDER=/path/to/your/projects
